Class JdbcUserServiceImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
      • org.eclipse.scada.configuration.world.osgi.impl.JdbcUserServiceImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Documentable, JdbcUserService

    public class JdbcUserServiceImpl
extends MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
implements JdbcUserService
    An implementation of the model object 'Jdbc User Service'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Short Description
    • Name
    • Jdbc Propeties
    • Jdbc Driver
    • Authorative
    • Find User Sql
    • Find Roles For User Sql
    • Update Password Sql
    • User Id Column Name
    • Password Column Name
    • Password Type
